方面的内部勺子。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;来自彭博社的更多信息&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;在您的收件箱中&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Moqi_v4rY_ir_7mvKtVdqETv-ME08nCgbzvdbbzcW-XN4wbwMvhlscBNPpYlm0AsADGJOv8JYatoh63sI9DzxHTGndYsFDs_uD-IF5WQxz0z5xcW6xduUYdnWeCR_e9nzG4hPt5ajEVrg4Jes4bsVIx8HfeP-pcSz578Lh3k9ocA78Crm2OGrU7uvDHgXE9e7eaqbB6NYKNPLRqSSJPl4TF62SMv5CpR0J8kogG7EmBPyevWO3vag8kqKTZ9wQldTmNOcvKt3TP3l2YUJ64-RP0IKg/BP44PBCCjOJBVNc8gS4NtMOgAef4AJwI/9"&gt;获得深入的技术&lt;/a&gt;和更多彭博技术新闻通讯：&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/AgWX6ES0JwOaJFI8qKcuP2zhT8-7pw1Isr5Kmr3nYPiB20Ms8LfOxKumiNlErTBECJcxYeus0hQkQVTBnobjViZR0UnKthkM6dXh5wm_ZksG3Kp1GCA1lBnaX0eDwJ158UAyblHrZzmhgYDhpX7DiO7DksJowGxX4PCfoGn5gV6Ad1aVrHLuz9r9hpVsmmrQcpvj_HYpvuUZVAJysFoNR2TR_RT4E44DNVB9wC-a97b6fwuBCA4hMTdTFGfNn4boFrku79HgvcAhPf3JMZmT0AVuCA/aMblaR_aXb190XVEByJTErsJX3Z-_m9F/9"&gt;网络公告&lt;/a&gt;，以覆盖黑客和网络活动的阴影世界&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/mabNST3FMIAup8y0RFDd-y0nu3w4E-EpcFLvy4NI7DZr5AmGZ00PtGm7rh81WrNYs5YfICzlta-rbumkmsPF5IOTwoxkD1sOGQJnFwAQhk97a0rY3k9zfBdD3GX839ZWDBVBUfhxU7P7AVQglrEZFQ7jMwnI-AyF9XZkSEesM9VzLCLJ35qnfka2D_T3GE1lv1z8pPNd7xJT0ZOEs3GNFaEom_nbEpjm6CDJSqAiDL3l1vh1P5eTwCiqQZTGQg28q3o25PfaLEv61i2ErAyh8uplOQ/loiHwtp0WYycecL67fV1Q4M7xkNcKaul/9"&gt;在视频游戏业务深处潜水的游戏&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-famil