href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/rzexww4ZV0bY7andKIImXzVvF0KhKu6SipkXA0eoH45da4ZjQTfc_z3zlRSaLK1DRN8OPiuihRGEL0DTnklheNjgYKa8WPJMelyWcwGbG1xxaI-iE5yFwoH3Ug0q7aP6wtgE8YqqD4v2RA4Ypj4JzHEYpzpP_JCA2ohP2bhmoKAEMUrqI1sCeSguO2XRVmxWT8oKN_-P6_Ibb-75CiDr7rEeQZqUAsIcR_Vk4iC9qW84KQQ0J-YyGRorkYuyJ1WJeelARosFn33GH4hQg2qgRBLYOA/QhtgtM3b3zkkPPzFSf9_Az96GQoV0Jhz/9" target="_blank"&gt;可能会在本周发表讲话&lt;/a&gt;，因为两国继续争论贸易。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/7Ui-k6EszDv1EXLLq21n24jIlgqGPH2NERZ2NvnrEAR5G-bko-JXAYSz0bZ8esvRqgf7pcC8iA8oVoLZTyc30jntEy0nZYNyqsKdt1mMEM6NkM9m_bVXxKdBo59VDJYkG7QxuxlU4V9C-jb-Rgr3b5zoU4qdPGi98URh4egNanrfo_MRAeoyLvnJJxAUcWJkIaupX_-8PhQrZGO5sM4xpB5BR6Gbe1giUZULza_ljypxxVtj64pvGSp6QS_3S3TU9JwUG3o0-rPj_cDmWqjsLf7kUw/D8CNQWEwRCGwBCfxHZBI8aObrGQJ6vd1/9" target="_blank"&gt;主要的粘性点&lt;/a&gt;似乎是关键的矿物质，美国官员抱怨北京并没有加快尖端电子产品所需的出口。在通讯故障和新的关税威胁中，与欧洲的贸易谈判&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/vIRNWEyjpcx4sdnws9bgHf9tPjD8pQwRBtJ8BCWXW1cQEx1neDtod0q9i13gua_E_OReMeMMxc5qeLbir5Ddfkd0pqkoo_lir-U6nuo76ftcvbUhSJJa4OPTys0tcUErE-34l9vE_gkBGprd6-0JRspeMK-WZnaNz1UaMJWTCd7gVyYejj8Bo5-8hlTaK966mOaaGbL3M-QJgl4-bsSucNFuK6EIgo8LnDrPEhAagEfAI9gNzj7u9dvByVrMYZgXDsCtWDD5-y8FhHaDSLSvrtnT6Q/L7HqD7Tq3WyH6fFmulI6zWJvNfJZWizV/9" target="_blank"&gt;也陷入困境&lt;/a&gt;。据前代理白宫参谋长说，如果与习近平的电话确实发生了，特朗普的交易风格&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/AbeogyzPPO98aLCsSqyF0UhMJ9lkz-q-PB9S6XwTCXojzXYQDCmNneS5GyYUM3fu8gV1Tq9rfO-BoaTINyOcaYCF_H19Mm8svYRWwlLoYJf4xb9BnJliLXFRxCg7_lqi0zDL0ASc3snkz51Iw5OvZOoIxeaEShRo-LR4L1Mfp_wEMLNwv0ZGCvGGXps-LvHePPlbM5D2HL0LNUeq6ngM2dZ94K2Czwho6F3BSsW_vXwXoAvXHg_ErPhN8_j7dVdqa7wzDfPUkuK7boAQleLMNh3PQg/wNpLdVzb8l94xQgcvFRbi5fYLKYYXXaa/9" target="_blank"&gt;不会影响中国领导人&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 16px 0px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; border-