%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;好吧，这种关税融化&lt;/strong&gt;并没有持续很长时间。中国&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/TShn7SNhwF1rebjb06BP-pbD0c2bK6vXMBJCCwhnPMqNnf7lFw0pfKXQfCWGJ345DPDsRcsS2_CxR42C3otS0ykp6wi_niMPfO4AvLXeiWieqm2ldk-zSltyZ8vDxhucjf2NrN_M9Eg8Z7_zz9d31XG6eLGhIoKxvxLTQBTNwGakVDNVU0Kr8iT2Sn8qjK3T9kK69qOf67sCwgHe_7R578ONW_Tutrn6ZddqNp-66-lfaYGSy8YrpD_fPSWZDfjzL2bieURUR9eQF_GuLzzze_UfYQ/ltJ5W24Ha3RqIcRwk8MGEft1UzavBhpU/9" target="_blank"&gt;指责美国&lt;/a&gt;违反了他们最近的贸易协定，并发誓要采取措施捍卫其利益，使&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/lJ7PaQWMJBZwNKmg6TGNOJCz63uGBHqlwMmjPPK_VKTG3aFuuxQ3bkMypIkbMiVSASAxKTc0obJE_ZCS_bxTAN1l5Snik99SpK7VQuoPcQV_W2O_MML_O4fMV2C_y0bxd9IHdlZf31rnELrW2obKfkEOF-zukqBnU-LluTTQmd3Ds8k1nBWuN9pLxS6HbLQb2l0CXh3SN-Rs2YeKgwfyvFQzL9TJkXVJ5r-fl25kmlowf24x1tB4TY6raUd9QaHFcEDKrmGVEMYtHK36MYDSDXL1fg/-W-7dCd615nbTI_spqo0YK5aigjsx1AA/9" target="_blank"&gt;领导人之间立即呼吁&lt;/a&gt;的前景（特朗普总统都希望。随着&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/X_CFz9zQ7kOzJEnzzKRMvNarMbycJ6owy43ycZ4jTWRd_-JabYhn4glcStiRDglkqO3v0DDA9_SgU1lA08CY_c1xsCvj2aosU5K8r3BcZBuO_WGW11hg65wvGs28pxaCW-vUX7aR2bzb2roN9rx-EYEWMPuVqWYFpMTKUupRjeiMCu6y3B5q0240jLBr0YOEMMV7ub2G3uI5TQQL09-j9KqC_sDIfREXORd6mp5qC6-YAi7_3N4f2OqKhpTkaeU6XIT3I-m6Op7yhiZlkv7AYrEYDA/ddgsjUmaDpUZFxFNXLaotp8llGzpF4Yy/9" target="_blank"&gt;交易周的开始，贸易战争延长的股权期货和美元的前景日益增加。&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;美元的前景&lt;/strong&gt;看起来不错。摩根士丹利（Morgan Stanley）表示，随着美国经济放缓，美联储降低了利率&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/AfZqtmYVXDHhlXQmzCV_W9leGR--PE_j5LCsYRoVMYoVGOZnZpuUVJ84ezeyjMe7g8i6oafh0v3HmL4dS_hobMW5UTfOeDbhO9u664Q2ePxiXmHaCLnrinN2zi2OjLj964ILr91u8lU6liq37ypU75GaqEOK0snh7JejmJTMVg-A1UxxaRrDu_RCSTjBhq7IAFzWZQVBuJ7lEJJotuti1v0r6G2eNbWK7GXreH6BNH7mFwLaVOIQsfWXmPSFw53MmLBFjoUTmo36a2P1vn8ztp-0Tw/J5ohdBMCCVkv3chN7ujk5StgrWx4CChT/9" target="_blank"&gt;，绿色的绿色可能会在明年中旬下降9％&lt;/a&gt; 。这一切都增加了这样的论点，即世界正在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/KY-6cW7XqpiYdSiyJTjpNK4epQuQ8Nm471ATkYZ_ddK5gJnkOrOueytwZImvawhA087pKvrpTUjnTeAt6jHlNcatbraka_iBeefXspvrXWg7p1GzWSOrhSzuO1-XNZKC0PjPzXi73KzSMMbAafGzrIwAP7IGiV0wEOGu4CIu2igreg7ncqdGAoaYeKNamqPNNZ4HntAsQdREkg1I_djdKkrKeyZvDX99F0XO_UJLEZZ_z5fHHg1CWUba-49KLS378Z7b4lDzysdErVmN2TiRzXrtPA/_3dnlqYkqaAS8WZD4hiqucWeCxYLqLgr/9" target="_blank"&gt;重新思考其对美元的依赖&lt;/a&gt;。而且，一些世界上最大的货币经理&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/biLOtZ-On0lSkvQaO3qabGU5FtLl88LwzM7e5a5wN3mK1atUl6a_Se8vHsjXzFVj7XgGTz2KqC5-X4jm4Cm0xqY_m4N4E31Z45Oqvujj_bwgYaeUSHcViavPxhBXK1goKZlhBA_LflsHyUSgUFDFb24TR32JiLpKy3lWelMiN06YLXEvjDs3iwcAEcvk-V8F5g8J933MXpCAuFviCGpQ3V91E88AzCwFosekiWF_oKvfkuDnZJx5D7usWhqhJ7KNPigG2Yp0VHVzWf8Yhq2BwU4v7Q/1LJn-cSlXe-EQJuyZJuzKpFYGCMn6xBb/9" target="_blank"&gt;正在避开长期以来的国债，而转而&lt;/a&gt;支持短期债务，而债务的利率较小。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/AdORfEJzTrPaw9mmurNunCSwMVUDuu15QW1lVVKjIxjo8ZwLT4QnES4E-GJqtI2-ZNLaA2tpHXaOd02Ua_xFlr4_k7j_YcmrBWdg5hDiJmcF8FnjrBegp2O2dAQ47xavTGmRp2ku9kVdh3-t_nalR2_C2eQXB0r0VSCX3JlXcwr6XPWRAfFtdsDOQQdAoETyw1-vFPwLFVymaX1ypZGWHv9QUHjJwIN92aXiUTuGff4gBfBubgn4dEhF93qUcv5PEGQ9AmCfz6_mYwqf92CnjyrRvQ/5X6gFtxSSgCl-wZoyFR5qhz7E9QSBH7E/9" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iDUWVAnfXu1M/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="alt" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iDUWVAnfXu1M/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" width="53