idia&lt;/strong&gt;在Big Tech的收入季节超过预期的收入季节，通过赢得了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/qsfOlqAYJGt4d7J14IUxGMzenSw_q0j_Q43VYUWNlxtvj2JNlcOYG-jbhrMmjErCm2RON5KeUWLUqnBL7Az8dCsiR7eMkxIwk1y9y4KR2j8wKZPREcv1jX-xRAAsG7f6saVp4dHDIQnwUtMmMQI51EaX6MIYN3ZFhjlcIEZuz_yGIAVfZjbIdi_jwg-NsCtCEwjzfLPTQmFY-IwQUEqSyxbkUroiaKVIi6O7JXi62y2V0ZuVnZtC4O7ujUGrVMjC4GVPmIIMotDOCJiKa9y8POYSIg/60DuMr2G5JOlJXnAXqkEweKCNwjHwiBd/9" target="_blank"&gt;强劲的收入前景&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;随着NVIDIA和MICROSOFT&lt;/strong&gt;逐渐回到近记录，交易员正在押注该集团有望取消更广泛的市场。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;首先，富兰克林首席市场策略师布雷特·尤因（Brett Ewing）说&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;：“这个坦克中还有&lt;/strong&gt;更多的汽油。”&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;彭博观点的&lt;/strong&gt;乔纳森·莱文（Jonathan Levin）在下面解释了为什么标准普尔500指数正在通过特朗普政策动荡巡游。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/h2IThQjZEIDdOdgILpo5khgUTJGJ8rbzMUnlO1WFTfkS_Y72y8gd0ERnYHz41oeGjx5Dt-KE0zfAxsLqkY7cR2dSSJ1ROlKe5uTrbSXpdYGx2OBstc_1SCC2dpkpCqySMF6xe78ZxcNk-9FeS_YSrW6Jvx2OY6McyLghot5Ee6EZDxatUyC2sZRL8Sdypg5cRRYQLYUzZQy8nnzTnm6UMuLjfU62X84RWQHP7MNq7vibdrStYLlQ4LZmIYH0mw8ufi6277RNOKAM7kWyzZzpLK493Q/bP7Nqy3pXrWxt7vos3EgeZbFEd1VmffD/9" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/is.IhjHmBcyc/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="alt" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/is.IhjHmBcyc/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;"